1
00:00:04,463 --> 00:00:06,215
Howard:
LIEUTENANT... IS IT TRUE
THE HUMAN REFORM LEAGUE

2
00:00:06,215 --> 00:00:08,425
FOUGHT A BATTLE WITH THE
GUNDAMS IN SPACE?

3
00:00:08,425 --> 00:00:09,760
YEAH.

4
00:00:09,760 --> 00:00:12,095
AND I HEARD THAT, JUDGING FROM
THE DEBRIS ALONE,

5
00:00:12,095 --> 00:00:14,264
OVER TWENTY TIERENS
WERE SERIOUSLY DAMAGED.

6
00:00:14,264 --> 00:00:15,766
(Whistles)

7
00:00:15,766 --> 00:00:17,768
NO WAY. KIND
OF SCARY JUST THINKING ABOUT

8
00:00:17,768 --> 00:00:20,145
GOING UP
AGAINST THOSE THINGS.

9
00:00:20,145 --> 00:00:22,231
YEAH, NO KIDDING.

10
00:00:22,231 --> 00:00:24,816
YEAH, WELL MOBILE SUIT
PERFORMANCE ISN'T THE ONLY THING

11
00:00:24,816 --> 00:00:27,527
THAT DETERMINES WHO'S GOING
TO WIN A FIGHT.

12
00:00:27,527 --> 00:00:29,112
I KNOW YOU'LL
DO ME PROUD...

13
00:00:29,112 --> 00:00:30,239
FLAG FIGHTERS.

14
00:00:32,783 --> 00:00:34,576
SO, THOSE SPECIAL
PARTICLES

15
00:00:34,576 --> 00:00:36,537
ARE ACTUALLY
DIVERSELY MUTABLE PHOTONS.

16
00:00:36,537 --> 00:00:38,247
YES, BUT THAT'S NOT ALL.

17
00:00:38,247 --> 00:00:40,249
THE GUNDAMS SEEM
TO BE PRODUCING THESE

18
00:00:40,249 --> 00:00:42,876
UNIQUE PARTICLES WITHIN
THEIR ENGINES.

19
00:00:42,876 --> 00:00:44,670
I DON'T KNOW HOW
ELSE TO EXPLAIN

20
00:00:44,670 --> 00:00:46,755
THEIR SEEMINGLY
LIMITLESS FLIGHT RANGE

21
00:00:46,755 --> 00:00:48,257
AND EXTENDED
OPERATION TIME.

22
00:00:48,257 --> 00:00:50,259
THAT MUST HAVE SOMETHING
TO DO WITH THE FACT THAT

23
00:00:50,259 --> 00:00:53,178
ONLY FOUR GUNDAMS HAVE
MADE AN APPEARANCE SO FAR.

24
00:00:53,178 --> 00:00:57,474
AEOLIA SCHENBERG WAS A
MAN OF SUPERHUMAN GENIUS.

25
00:00:57,474 --> 00:01:00,060
TO THINK HE DISCOVERED THIS
PARTICLE AND ESTABLISHED

26
00:01:00,060 --> 00:01:02,396
ITS BASIC THEORY
OVER TWO CENTURIES AGO.

27
00:01:03,814 --> 00:01:05,274
HMM...

28
00:01:05,274 --> 00:01:08,193
WHY WOULD A MAN LIKE THAT
INITIATE SUCH AN UNREALISTIC

29
00:01:08,193 --> 00:01:10,946
PROJECT AS THE ELIMINATION
OF WAR FROM THE WORLD?

30
00:01:10,946 --> 00:01:13,949
TO WARN HUMANITY WHO
SEEM ON THE VERGE

31
00:01:13,949 --> 00:01:16,451
OF BRINGING THE SEEDS
OF WAR UP INTO SPACE.

32
00:01:16,451 --> 00:01:20,122
AT LEAST, THAT'S
HOW I SEE IT.

33
00:01:20,122 --> 00:01:30,173
♪

34
00:01:30,173 --> 00:01:50,193
♪

35
00:01:50,193 --> 00:02:10,213
