38
00:03:01,223 --> 00:03:03,266
Tieria:
IN THE MILITARY OPERATION

39
00:03:03,266 --> 00:03:05,435
THAT WAS CARRIED OUT
BY THE HUMAN REFORM LEAGUE,

40
00:03:05,435 --> 00:03:07,646
KYRIOS WAS NEARLY CAPTURED
AND NADLEEH WAS

41
00:03:07,646 --> 00:03:09,231
REVEALED TO THE ENEMY.

42
00:03:09,231 --> 00:03:11,483
SUMERAGI LEE NORIEGA,
AS COMMANDER

43
00:03:11,483 --> 00:03:14,319
OF THE OPERATION,
EVERYTHING THAT HAS HAPPENED

44
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:15,654
IS YOUR FAULT.

45
00:03:15,654 --> 00:03:18,740
I AM SORRY. BUT AS YOU KNOW,
I'M ONLY HUMAN,

46
00:03:18,740 --> 00:03:21,410
THERE ARE TIMES
WHEN I DO MAKE MISTAKES.

47
00:03:21,410 --> 00:03:23,412
THAT'S NO EXCUSE FOR WHAT
OCCURRED HERE.

48
00:03:23,412 --> 00:03:25,831
DO YOU KNOW HOW MUCH THIS
WILL SET THE PLAN BACK?

49
00:03:25,831 --> 00:03:26,998
YOU'RE THE ONE
WHO PANICKED

50
00:03:26,998 --> 00:03:29,084
AND SHOWED
NADLEEH TO THE ENEMY.

51
00:03:29,084 --> 00:03:30,961
IF I HADN'T, THEY'D
HAVE CAPTURED ME.

52
00:03:30,961 --> 00:03:33,046
THAT MAY BE SO,
BUT YOU'RE STILL

53
00:03:33,046 --> 00:03:34,297
PARTIALLY
RESPONSIBLE FOR IT.

54
00:03:34,297 --> 00:03:36,925
YOU CAN'T BLAME ALL OF THIS
ON MISS SUMERAGI.

55
00:03:36,925 --> 00:03:39,886
COUNT YOUR BLESSINGS
THAT YOU'RE STILL ALIVE.

56
00:03:39,886 --> 00:03:43,473
I'LL BE GIVING VEDA'S COMMANDS
TOP PRIORITY FROM NOW ON.

57
00:03:43,473 --> 00:03:44,850
EXCUSE ME.

58
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,813
(Sighs)

59
00:03:49,813 --> 00:03:51,022
WELL, THAT WAS
SURE TENSE.

60
00:03:51,022 --> 00:03:52,816
HE DIDN'T HAVE TO COME
IN HERE WITH

61
00:03:52,816 --> 00:03:55,277
AN ATTITUDE AND SAY IT IN
FRONT OF EVERYONE LIKE THAT.

62
00:03:55,277 --> 00:03:58,363
I THINK IT'S CUTE HOW UPTIGHT
THE GUY IS...

63
00:03:58,363 --> 00:04:01,116
HE'S ANGRY WITH HIMSELF
SO HE TAKES IT OUT ON OTHERS.

64
00:04:04,286 --> 00:04:06,413
(Thinking):
THAT MACHINE...
A HIGH‐MOBILITY

65
00:04:06,413 --> 00:04:09,249
SUPER‐SOLDIER
VERSION OF THE TIEREN.

66
00:04:09,249 --> 00:04:11,710
THERE'S NO DOUBT ABOUT IT.

67
00:04:11,710 --> 00:04:14,546
THAT PILOT IS JUST LIKE ME.

68
00:04:14,546 --> 00:04:16,298
THEY'RE NOT STILL WORKING ON
THAT PROJECT...ARE THEY?

69
00:04:18,884 --> 00:04:21,219
THAT ACCURSED PROJECT.

70
00:04:29,019 --> 00:04:31,396
Commander #4A:
THE DATA COLLECTED ON THE
WINGED GUNDAM

71
00:04:31,396 --> 00:04:33,356
DURING ITS CAPTURE,

72
00:04:33,356 --> 00:04:35,901
IMAGES FROM THE
TIERENS' MISSION RECORDERS

73
00:04:35,901 --> 00:04:38,487
OF THE CELESTIAL BEING'S
MOTHER SHIP

74
00:04:38,487 --> 00:04:41,531
AND THE BIG
ONE SHEDDING ITS ARMOR.

75
00:04:41,531 --> 00:04:45,118
IT'S SIMPLY NOT WORTH THE
COST OF SEVERAL HUNDRED

76
00:04:45,118 --> 00:04:47,704
THOUSAND PROBES AND
MORE THAN TWENTY TIERENS.

77
00:04:47,704 --> 00:04:49,623
I HAVE NO EXCUSE, SIR.

78
00:04:49,623 --> 00:04:52,375
I AM PREPARED TO FACE
DISCIPLINARY ACTION.

79
00:04:52,375 --> 00:04:56,338
I HAVE NO PLANS TO RELIEVE YOU.
AND YOU CAN NOT RESIGN.

80
00:04:56,338 --> 00:04:57,756
HMM?

81
00:04:57,756 --> 00:05:00,175
IT'S TRUE THE OPERATION
WAS A FAILURE...

82
00:05:00,175 --> 00:05:03,887
BUT THAT HASN'T CHANGED MY
EVALUATION OF YOU ONE BIT.

83
00:05:03,887 --> 00:05:05,972
THE GUNDAMS' ABILITIES
SIMPLY SURPASSED

84
00:05:05,972 --> 00:05:07,974
ALL OF OUR
EXPECTATIONS.

85
00:05:07,974 --> 00:05:09,976
EXCUSE ME, SIR,
BUT WE STILL DON'T KNOW

86
00:05:09,976 --> 00:05:11,770
WHAT THEIR TRUE LIMITS ARE.

87
00:05:11,770 --> 00:05:14,731
CONTINUING THIS CAPTURE
OPERATION COULD BE VERY COSTLY‐‐

88
00:05:14,731 --> 00:05:18,109
I'M AWARE OF THAT AS WELL.
THE CHAIRMAN IS

89
00:05:18,109 --> 00:05:20,862
CURRENTLY CONDUCTING SECRET
NEGOTIATIONS WITH THE UNION.

90
00:05:20,862 --> 00:05:22,364
TALKS WITH THE UNION?

91
00:05:22,364 --> 00:05:25,283
THIS MEANS THAT THE
CELESTIAL BEING SITUATION

92
00:05:25,283 --> 00:05:28,119
IS MOVING TO THE NEXT
PHASE OF ENGAGEMENT.

93
00:05:29,079 --> 00:05:30,872
Ivan:
LIEUTENANT PERIES...

94
00:05:30,872 --> 00:05:32,499
PLEASE,
AVENGE LIEUTENANT MING

95
00:05:32,499 --> 00:05:34,125
IN THE NEXT OPERATION...

96
00:05:34,125 --> 00:05:36,253
NO... AVENGE ALL
OUR COMRADES!

97
00:05:36,253 --> 00:05:39,256
I WILL COMPLETE MY MISSIONS
THE BEST THAT I CAN.

98
00:05:39,256 --> 00:05:41,341
BECAUSE THAT IS
ESSENTIALLY

99
00:05:41,341 --> 00:05:43,885
THE ONLY REASON THAT
I AM PERMITTED TO EXIST.

100
00:05:45,053 --> 00:05:46,805
(Allelujah on recording):
STAY BACK!

101
00:05:46,805 --> 00:05:48,723
(Screams)

102
00:05:48,723 --> 00:05:51,768
AS THE LIEUTENANT'S TAOZI
APPROACHES,

103
00:05:51,768 --> 00:05:55,480
THE GUNDAM PILOT
EXPERIENCES INCREASED PAIN.

104
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:58,441
CLEARLY, THE PILOT IS
BEING AFFECTED

105
00:05:58,441 --> 00:06:01,236
BY THE QUANTUM BRAIN WAVES.

106
00:06:02,612 --> 00:06:04,823
(Computer beeps)

107
00:06:04,823 --> 00:06:07,909
THERE IS ONE.
TEST SUBJECT E‐57.

108
00:06:07,909 --> 00:06:11,329
E‐57. AFTER QUANTUM
BRAIN WAVE TREATMENT.

109
00:06:11,329 --> 00:06:14,249
NEW PERSONALITY MANIFESTED
FEROCIOUS TENDENCIES...

110
00:06:14,249 --> 00:06:18,295
AFTER DATA
WAS COLLECTED... DISPOSED OF.

111
00:06:18,295 --> 00:06:19,921
THIS ISN'T GOOD.

112
00:06:19,921 --> 00:06:21,673
IF THE TOP BRASS FINDS
OUT ABOUT THIS THERE'S‐‐

113
00:06:21,673 --> 00:06:23,300
(Gasps)

114
00:06:23,300 --> 00:06:24,801
DID YOU FIND OUT ANYTHING

115
00:06:24,801 --> 00:06:26,553
FROM EXAMINING THE
TAOZI'S MISSION RECORDER?

116
00:06:26,553 --> 00:06:27,762
WELL...

117
00:06:27,762 --> 00:06:29,723
NOTHING SIGNIFICANT YET, SIR.

118
00:06:29,723 --> 00:06:31,516
I BELIEVE THE
GUNDAM PILOT

119
00:06:31,516 --> 00:06:33,560
AND LIEUTENANT
PERIES ARE THE SAME TYPE.

120
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:36,813
I CAN'T RULE OUT THE POSSIBILITY
THAT OTHER COUNTRIES

121
00:06:36,813 --> 00:06:40,025
MIGHT BE RESEARCHING QUANTUM
BRAIN WAVE TREATMENT AS WELL.

122
00:06:40,025 --> 00:06:42,068
IF THEY ARE,
THEN IT JUST SHOWS

123
00:06:42,068 --> 00:06:44,654
HOW TWISTED THIS WORLD
REALLY IS.

124
00:06:44,654 --> 00:06:48,783
I'M AFRAID I HAVE TO AGREE WITH
YOU ON THAT POINT, COLONEL.

125
00:06:52,871 --> 00:06:55,248
WHAT SHOULD I DO?
SHOULD I REPORT THIS?

126
00:06:55,248 --> 00:06:56,875
OR SHOULD I JUST‐‐

127
00:06:56,875 --> 00:06:59,002
THERE'S ONLY ONE
THING YOU CAN DO!

128
00:06:59,002 --> 00:07:00,462
HALLELUJAH.

129
00:07:00,462 --> 00:07:03,048
THAT DETESTABLE LABORATORY IS
STILL IN EXISTENCE

130
00:07:03,048 --> 00:07:05,258
AND IT'S
STILL CHURNING OUT PEOPLE

131
00:07:05,258 --> 00:07:07,469
LIKE YOU AND ME ONE AFTER
THE OTHER...

132
00:07:07,469 --> 00:07:11,014
WHICH MAKES THAT INSTITUTE
GUILTY OF PROMOTING WAR.

133
00:07:11,014 --> 00:07:15,560
YOU WANT ME TO DESTROY IT?
AND THE PEOPLE LIKE US.

134
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,646
IS THE KIND‐HEARTED
MR. ALLELUJAH

135
00:07:17,646 --> 00:07:19,981
TOO GOOD
FOR THAT KIND OF WORK?

136
00:07:19,981 --> 00:07:21,900
THEN HAND YOUR BODY
OVER TO ME,

137
00:07:21,900 --> 00:07:24,527
I'LL DEAL WITH
THE ISSUE REAL QUICK.

138
00:07:24,527 --> 00:07:26,154
JUST LIKE I DID BEFORE.

139
00:07:26,154 --> 00:07:28,448
(Child's voice)
ARE WE GOING TO DIE?

140
00:07:28,448 --> 00:07:32,827
OH, NO! I DON'T WANT TO DIE!
ALLELUJAH! ALLELUJAH!

141
00:07:32,827 --> 00:07:34,829
IT'S NO GOOD!

142
00:07:34,829 --> 00:07:37,123
YOU'RE GOING TO DIE!

143
00:07:37,123 --> 00:07:39,125
ALLELUJAH, PLEASE‐‐

144
00:07:39,125 --> 00:07:41,378
NO... MY NAME IS‐‐

145
00:07:41,378 --> 00:07:42,796
(Gasps)

146
00:07:42,796 --> 00:07:44,172
NO, FORGET IT,
HALLELUJAH.

147
00:07:44,172 --> 00:07:46,049
WE DON'T HAVE TO
KILL ANYONE!

148
00:07:46,049 --> 00:07:48,051
WE COULD JUST
TAKE THEM INTO CUSTODY!

149
00:07:48,051 --> 00:07:50,387
WHAT FUTURE DOES
A PERSON WHO WAS REBUILT

150
00:07:50,387 --> 00:07:52,639
FOR COMBAT POSSIBLY HAVE?

151
00:07:52,639 --> 00:07:54,891
YOU KNOW THE ANSWER TO THAT
BETTER THAN ANYONE.

152
00:07:54,891 --> 00:07:59,270
YEAH, CELESTIAL BEING'S
MR. GUNDAM MEISTER.

153
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:02,357
YOU'RE WRONG! THE REAL
REASON I CAME HERE WAS‐‐

154
00:08:02,357 --> 00:08:04,275
BECAUSE THE ONLY THING
YOU CAN DO IS FIGHT!

155
00:08:04,275 --> 00:08:05,485
NO!

156
00:08:05,485 --> 00:08:07,529
BECAUSE THAT IS OUR DESTINY!

157
00:08:07,529 --> 00:08:09,406
YOU'RE WRONG!
I'M NOT...

158
00:08:09,406 --> 00:08:10,407
(Gasps)

159
00:08:10,407 --> 00:08:11,533
SETSUNA...

160
00:08:11,533 --> 00:08:14,327
SOMETHING WRONG?

161
00:08:14,327 --> 00:08:16,705
UH, NO...NOTHING'S WRONG.

162
00:08:19,416 --> 00:08:21,835
Alejandro:
I UNDERSTAND THE CONSTRUCTION
OF THE RECEIVER ANTENNAS

163
00:08:21,835 --> 00:08:23,670
HAS FALLEN BEHIND SCHEDULE.

164
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:26,715
Marina:
THE CONSTRUCTION HAS BEEN
INTERRUPTED A NUMBER OF TIMES.

165
00:08:26,715 --> 00:08:29,551
THERE ARE SOME ELEMENTS
AMONG MY PEOPLE

166
00:08:29,551 --> 00:08:31,761
WHO ARE OPPOSED TO
SOLAR POWER GENERATION.

167
00:08:31,761 --> 00:08:34,305
PLEASE, WE'D LIKE YOU
TO MAKE THE SAFETY

168
00:08:34,305 --> 00:08:36,266
OF OUR ENGINEERS
YOUR TOP PRIORITY.

169
00:08:36,266 --> 00:08:38,893
IF SOMETHING HAPPENED WE'D
REALLY HAVE NO CHOICE

170
00:08:38,893 --> 00:08:40,770
BUT TO LEAVE
YOUR COUNTRY.

171
00:08:40,770 --> 00:08:43,606
I UNDERSTAND AND I'VE CONVEYED
YOUR CONCERNS TO THE ARMY.

172
00:08:43,606 --> 00:08:45,859
YOUR HIGHNESS...
WHY NOT TAKE SOME TIME

173
00:08:45,859 --> 00:08:49,070
TO PAY A COURTESY VISIT
TO THE CONSTRUCTION SITE?

174
00:08:49,070 --> 00:08:51,031
IT WOULD GREATLY
IMPROVE THE MORALE

175
00:08:51,031 --> 00:08:53,116
OF THE SOLDIERS AND
ENGINEERS‐‐

176
00:08:53,116 --> 00:08:54,909
SO THAT SHE CAN
BE ASSASSINATED?

177
00:08:54,909 --> 00:08:56,161
Marina:
SHIRIN!

178
00:08:56,161 --> 00:08:58,580
AMBASSADOR CORNER,
WHY DID THE UNITED NATIONS

179
00:08:58,580 --> 00:09:02,083
DECIDE TO GRANT TECHNICAL
ASSISTANCE TO AZADISTAN?

180
00:09:02,083 --> 00:09:03,793
IN THE MIDDLE EAST
THERE ARE MANY COUNTRIES

181
00:09:03,793 --> 00:09:05,795
THAT
ARE TECHNOLOGICALLY BACKWARDS.

182
00:09:05,795 --> 00:09:07,797
SO WHY WOULD YOU HELP US?

183
00:09:07,797 --> 00:09:11,384
THE SIMPLEST ANSWER IS THAT
YOU REQUESTED OUR ASSISTANCE.

184
00:09:11,384 --> 00:09:13,720
THE UNITED NATIONS WISHES TO
EXTEND ITS SUPPORT

185
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:15,263
TO ALL THE
LANDS OF THE MIDDLE EAST,

186
00:09:15,263 --> 00:09:16,931
AND WE WOULD LIKE TO
MAKE A MODEL CASE

187
00:09:16,931 --> 00:09:19,100
OUT OF THE
KINGDOM OF AZADISTAN.

188
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:22,729
AND THE EXISTENCE OF CELESTIAL
BEING IS A CONCERN AS WELL.

189
00:09:22,729 --> 00:09:24,731
CELESTIAL BEING...

190
00:09:24,731 --> 00:09:27,066
THEY SEEK THE ERADICATION
OF WAR

191
00:09:27,066 --> 00:09:29,611
AND SINCE THE MIDDLE
EAST IS PLAGUED BY PERPETUAL,

192
00:09:29,611 --> 00:09:33,198
ALBEIT SMALL, CONFLICTS, THEIR
INTERVENTION IS INEVITABLE.

193
00:09:33,198 --> 00:09:35,450
RATHER THAN SENDING
ASSISTANCE TO REBUILD,

194
00:09:35,450 --> 00:09:37,494
I BELIEVE IT IS FAR
MORE BENEFICIAL

195
00:09:37,494 --> 00:09:40,121
TO HELP ALLEVIATE THE
CONFLICTS IN THE FIRST PLACE.

196
00:09:40,121 --> 00:09:42,999
THAT'S A NOBLE
SENTIMENT, INDEED.

197
00:09:42,999 --> 00:09:45,335
AMBASSADOR...
CAN YOU SWEAR BY YOUR GOD

198
00:09:45,335 --> 00:09:47,879
THAT THOSE FEELINGS
AND SENTIMENTS ARE TRUE?

199
00:09:47,879 --> 00:09:51,424
ABSOLUTELY. AND
BY YOUR GOD AS WELL...

200
00:09:51,424 --> 00:09:53,343
FOR AZADISTAN'S FUTURE.

201
00:09:53,343 --> 00:09:54,636
(Ice clinks)

202
00:09:54,636 --> 00:09:56,679
WHAT IS IT, ALLELUJAH?

203
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:58,640
LET ME GUESS, YOU'RE
ANGRY WITH ME TOO?

204
00:09:58,640 --> 00:10:00,141
YOU'VE BEEN
THROUGH A LOT,

205
00:10:00,141 --> 00:10:02,435
SO I WOULDN'T BLAME
YOU ONE BIT.

206
00:10:02,435 --> 00:10:05,605
I'M SORRY FOR BEING SUCH
A LOUSY TACTICAL FORECASTER.

207
00:10:05,605 --> 00:10:07,524
UH, ARE YOU DRUNK?

208
00:10:07,524 --> 00:10:09,150
IS THAT A PROBLEM?

209
00:10:09,150 --> 00:10:11,027
MAYBE YOU SHOULD
THINK ABOUT TAKING IT EASY.

210
00:10:11,027 --> 00:10:13,321
NO WAY. THIS IS THE
ONLY THING

211
00:10:13,321 --> 00:10:15,365
THAT MAKES ME
WANT TO KEEP ON LIVING.

212
00:10:16,574 --> 00:10:18,701
LISTEN...IF YOU DON'T
HAVE ANYTHING‐‐

213
00:10:18,701 --> 00:10:21,329
I HAVE A PROPOSAL FOR
A MISSION PLAN

214
00:10:21,329 --> 00:10:22,747
I WANT TO
RUN BY YOU AND VEDA.

215
00:10:22,747 --> 00:10:24,707
A MISSION PLAN?

216
00:10:24,707 --> 00:10:27,210
YES, IT'S AN
ARMED INTERVENTION MISSION

217
00:10:27,210 --> 00:10:29,212
AGAINST AN INSTITUTE
THAT PROMOTES WAR.

218
00:10:29,212 --> 00:10:32,298
THIS INSTITUTE IS A VERY
IMPORTANT PLACE FROM MY PAST.

219
00:10:32,298 --> 00:10:35,552
I'VE COLLECTED DETAILED
DATA ON IT.

220
00:10:35,552 --> 00:10:39,222
PLEASE TAKE A LOOK
AT IT WHEN YOU'RE SOBER.

221
00:10:39,222 --> 00:10:41,015
EXCUSE ME.

222
00:10:41,015 --> 00:10:42,809
(Door slides open)

223
00:10:42,809 --> 00:10:44,269
(Door closes)

224
00:10:44,269 --> 00:10:45,937
HUH?

225
00:10:45,937 --> 00:10:49,691
HUMAN REFORM LEAGUE,
